  </header>

  <!-- Login -->
  <div id="login">
    <section id="main-login" class="container">
      <header class="login-header">
        <h2 class="align-center-v">
          <img src="/public/img/logos/header.svg" class="login-logo" />
        </h2>
        <p id="title-sub">
          A place to play <strong>Hanab</strong> online,<br />
          a cooperative card game of logic and reasoning
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-8 off-2 login-box">
          <section id="loading" class="box align-center">
            <h3>Loading...</h3>
            <p>{{= it.projectName }} is loading. Please wait!</p>
            <img src="/public/img/ajax.gif" />
          </section>

          <section id="firefox-warning" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Warning!</h3>
            <p>
              You are using Firefox.<br />
              Firefox is incredibly slow at drawing Canvas-based graphics.<br />
              For your sanity, please use Chrome or Chromium when using this
              website.
            </p>
            <button id="firefox-warning-button" class="button align-center">
              OK
            </button>
          </section>

          <section id="sign-in" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Sign In / Create Account</h3>
            <p>
              To create a new account, simply login with a new username and
              select a password.<br />
              Do <strong>NOT</strong> reuse any of your
              <a
                href="https://github.com/Hanabi-Live/hanabi-live/blob/main/docs/passwords.md"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >previous passwords</a
              >!
            </p>
            <form id="login-form">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-1 off-2">
                  <i class="fas fa-user fa-2x login-icon"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="col-7">
                  <input
                    id="login-username"
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Username"
                    autofocus
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="padding0p75"></div>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-1 off-2">
                  <i class="fas fa-key fa-2x login-icon"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="col-7">
                  <input
                    id="login-password"
                    type="password"
                    placeholder="Password"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="padding0p75"></div>
              <div id="change-password-container" class="hidden">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-1 off-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-sync fa-2x login-icon"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-7">
                    <input
                      id="change-password"
                      type="password"
                      placeholder="New Password"
                    />
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <br />
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-7 off-3">
                  <a id="login-button" class="button fit icon fa-sign-in-alt"
                    >Sign In</a
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="col-1">
                  <img
                    id="login-ajax"
                    class="hidden"
                    src="/public/img/ajax.gif"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-7 off-3">
                  <p id="login-alert" class="hidden"></p>
                  <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                    <a id="change-password-link" href="#">Change password</a>
                    |
                    <a href="/password-reset">Forgot password?</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </form>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>

      <br />

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-8 off-2">
          <p class="login-text">
            This site has no affiliation with the card game Hanabi, no
            affiliation with Antoine Bauza (the creator of Hanabi), and no
            affiliation with any of the the real-life publishers of Hanabi (of
            which there are many).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-8 off-2">
          <p class="login-text">
            This website is free of charge, has no advertisements, and is not
            monetized in any way. Since this website is inspired by Hanabi, we
            urge you to purchase a physical copy of that game if you enjoy
            playing the variants of it online.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-8 off-2">
          <p class="login-text">
            Discord is a voice and text chat application that you can run in a
            browser.<br />
            If the server is down, you can probably find out why in
            <a href="https://discord.gg/FADvkJp">the Discord server</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 align-center">
          <a href="https://discord.gg/FADvkJp">
            <img id="title-discord" src="/public/img/discord.png" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- Tutorial -->
  <div id="tutorial" class="hidden">
    <section id="main-tutorial" class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-10 off-1">
          <section id="tutorial-1" class="box align-center">
            <h3>Welcome!</h3>
            <p>
              It looks like you are logging on to
              <em>{{= it.projectName }}</em> for the first time. There are some
              things you should know.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6">
                <a
                  id="tutorial-yes"
                  class="button fit icon fa-question-circle"
                >
                  Give me a basic rundown.
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-no" class="button fit icon fa-sign-in-alt">
                  I already know how everything works.
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-2" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>The Rules</h3>
            <p>Do you already know how to play?</p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-2-yes" class="button fit icon fa-check"
                  >Yup.</a
                >
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-2-no" class="button fit icon fa-times"
                  >Nope.</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-2-1" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>The Rules</h3>
            <p>
              Good, because the website assumes that you already know how to
              play.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12 align-center">
                <a id="tutorial-2-1-ok" class="button icon fa-check"
                  >Ok, what's next?</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-2-2" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>The Rules</h3>
            <p>
              Well, unfortunately the website does not have a tutorial mode or
              anything like that. You will have to learn
              <a
                href="https://github.com/Hanabi-Live/hanabi-live/blob/main/docs/rules.md"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >the rules</a
              >
              on your own. So read those, or try watching
              <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VrFCekQb4nY"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                this video explanation </a
              >.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12 align-center">
                <a id="tutorial-2-2-ok" class="button icon fa-check">
                  Ok, I'll learn the rules on my own.
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-3" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Using the Website</h3>
            <p>
              Getting a game going should be fairly straightforward:<br />
              1) Click on the "Create Game" button in the top navigation
              bar.<br />
              2) Other people join the game by clicking on the row in the list
              of games.<br />
              3) Then, you click on the "Start Game" button.
            </p>
            <p>
              Once the game has started:<br />
              1) Play a card by clicking and dragging it to the stacks in the
              center of the screen.<br />
              2) Discard a card by clicking and dragging it to the
              bottom-right-hand corner.<br />
              3) Give a clue by clicking the buttons in the middle of the
              screen.<br />
            </p>
            <p>
              For more detailed info, click on the "Help" button on the top
              navigation bar.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12 align-center">
                <a id="tutorial-3-ok" class="button icon fa-check"
                  >Ok, that sounds easy.</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-4" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Other Players</h3>
            <p>
              You can't play by yourself. Do you already have a team / a group
              of players to play with?
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-4-yes" class="button fit icon fa-check"
                  >Yup.</a
                >
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-4-no" class="button fit icon fa-times"
                  >Nope.</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-4-1" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Other Players</h3>
            <p>
              Good, because this website is mostly used with people who
              already have a team.<br />
              Good luck and enjoy the website!
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12 align-center">
                <a id="tutorial-4-1-ok" class="button icon fa-sign-in-alt"
                  >Thanks.</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-5" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Other Players</h3>
            <p>
              This game is a lot like Chess in that it is easy to learn, but
              hard to master, even after spending hundreds of hours playing.
            </p>
            <p>
              Are you looking to play a few casual one-off games?<br />
              Or, are you looking to "get into" the game and have a permanent
              team to learn from and grow with?
            </p>
            <a id="tutorial-5-casual" class="button icon fa-dice-one fit">
              I'm not super into this, so I just want to play a few one-off
              games.
            </a>
            <br /><br />
            <a id="tutorial-5-expert" class="button icon fa-dice-six fit">
              I love this game and would be willing to spend a lot of time to
              play with experienced players.
            </a>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-5-1" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Other Players</h3>
            <p>
              Unfortunately, finding quick games with strangers on the website
              is difficult because it is mostly used by people who already
              have a team. You can always try to join random games with other
              people, but don't be offended if people don't want to play with
              strangers.
            </p>
            <p>
              It used to be easy to find pick-up games on
              <a
                href="https://en.boardgamearena.com/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >Board Game Arena</a
              >, but not so many people play on there anymore because there is
              a pseudo-paywall (as of December 2020). You can try to find
              pick-up games on BGA, or you can try your luck in the lobby
              here.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12">
                <a id="tutorial-5-1-lobby" class="button icon fa-sign-in-alt">
                  Take me to the lobby for now.
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-6" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Other Players</h3>
            <p>
              That's good to hear. In general, the website is mostly used by
              people who already have a team, so finding quick games with
              strangers can be difficult. If you are interested in doing some
              prep work, I would like to welcome you to play with my group,
              the
              <em>H-Group</em>. We have been playing the game for many years,
              but we could always use new players.
            </p>
            <p></p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-6-ok" class="button icon fa-question-circle">
                  Ok, how do I join the H-Group?
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-6-lobby" class="button icon fa-sign-in-alt">
                  I'll pass, just take me to the lobby.
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-7" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Voice Chat</h3>
            <p>
              After my group finishes a game, we all get together in a voice
              chat to review it. This is important - everyone gets to learn
              from their mistakes and everyone can become more synchronized.
              As you may imagine, using a voice chat is much more productive
              than everyone typing text-snippets at each other.
            </p>
            <p>
              Do you have a working microphone and are you able to voice chat?
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-7-yes" class="button icon fa-check"> Yup. </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-7-no" class="button icon fa-times"> Nope. </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-7-1" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Voice Chat</h3>
            <p>
              That's too bad. Doing post-game reviews without a microphone is
              a real pain. Remember that if you do not have a desktop
              microphone or a headset, you can also use the Discord app on a
              cell phone. If you do not have a cell phone, you could always
              grab a cheap microphone from a local electronics store.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-7-1-microphone" class="button icon fa-check">
                  I think I can get a microphone after all.
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <a id="tutorial-7-1-lobby" class="button icon fa-sign-in-alt">
                  I'll pass, just take me to the lobby.
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="tutorial-8" class="box align-center hidden">
            <h3>Some Basic Conventions</h3>
            <p>
              If you try to play with our group and don't understand what our
              clues mean, things won't go well. We ask that you spend some
              time and read the
              <a
                href="https://hanabi.github.io/beginner"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                H-Group beginners guide </a
              >. It shouldn't take all that long. And the guide has further
              instructions about how to get games going with members of the
              group.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12">
                <a id="tutorial-8-ok" class="button icon fa-sign-in-alt">
                  I'll read the guide, thanks. Take me to the lobby.
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- Lobby -->
  <div id="lobby" class="container max hidden">
    <div id="lobby-top-half" class="row lobby-half toggle-active">
      <div class="col-12">
        <!-- The "games" table (all current games) -->
        <section id="lobby-games" class="box align-center-v">
          <h3 id="lobby-games-no">No current games.</h3>
          <div
            id="lobby-games-table-container"
            class="hidden lobby-table-container"
          >
            <h3 class="lobby-title">List of games</h3>
            <table id="lobby-games-table" class="alt">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Name</th>
                  <th># of Players</th>
                  <th>Variant</th>
                  <th>Options</th>
                  <th>Status</th>
                  <th>Players</th>
                  <th>Spectators</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="lobby-games-table-tbody"></tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- The "pregame" table -->
        <section id="lobby-pregame" class="box hidden">
          <div class="lobby-pregame-container">
            <div id="lobby-pregame-left" class="lobby-pregame-info">
              <h4 class="padding0p5">
                <strong><i class="fas fa-signature"></i>&nbsp; Name:</strong
                ><br />
                <span id="lobby-pregame-name"></span>
              </h4>
              <h4 class="padding0p5">
                <strong><i class="fas fa-rainbow"></i>&nbsp; Variant:</strong
                ><br />
                <span id="lobby-pregame-variant"></span>
              </h4>
              <h4 class="padding0p5">
                <strong><i class="fas fa-users"></i>&nbsp; Players:</strong
                ><br />
                <span id="lobby-pregame-seats"></span>
              </h4>
              <h4 class="padding0p5">
                <span id="lobby-pregame-options-title">Options:</span><br />
                <ul id="lobby-pregame-options"></ul>
              </h4>
              <h4 class="padding0p5">
                <strong
                  ><i class="fas fa-glasses"></i>&nbsp; Spectators:</strong
                ><br />
                <ul id="lobby-pregame-spectators"></ul>
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div class="lobby-pregame-players">
              <div
                id="lobby-pregame-player-1"
                class="lobby-pregame-player"
              ></div>
              <div
                id="lobby-pregame-player-2"
                class="lobby-pregame-player"
              ></div>
              <div
                id="lobby-pregame-player-3"
                class="lobby-pregame-player"
              ></div>
              <div
                id="lobby-pregame-player-4"
                class="lobby-pregame-player"
              ></div>
              <div
                id="lobby-pregame-player-5"
                class="lobby-pregame-player"
              ></div>
              <div
                id="lobby-pregame-player-6"
                class="lobby-pregame-player"
              ></div>
